  "body": "## Problem \r\n\r\nThe read/unread toggle button is currently behaving as a toggle that **only** displays either read or unread notifications.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/46027/198122312-1303f3fb-3c2f-4059-a187-687ad7122dc9.png\" width=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe toggle button should display either unread notifications or notifications in any state (both read and unread).\r\n\r\n#### Resources\r\n\r\n- https://www.figma.com/file/eDfxTa9IoaCMUy5cLTp0ys/Shell-for-Mobile?node-id=451%3A18681\r\n",
