    "body": "> @ilmotta I'm a bit lost, where do I find this toggle in the app currently?\r\n\r\n@rasom, This bug is only applicable for the new Activity Center, and in order to see it, you need to enable the flag `status-im.utils.config/new-activity-center-enabled?` (disabled by default).\r\n\r\nOn a side note, I still think we should keep the flag disabled by default until we implement a couple more fixes/features in the new AC, so that we don't disrupt other people's workflows using the old AC. Hopefully next month we get there ;)",
